<section id="Deleting_a_Domain" remap="TID_44541">
	<title>Deleting a Domain</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Delete a Domain</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Automate</guimenu><guisubmenu>Explorer</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. The default view is the Datastore.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the Domain that you want to delete.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>(Configuration)</guilabel>, then 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1861.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>(Remove This Domain)</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				A window to confirm the removal of Domain appears.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guilabel>OK</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<formalpara>
		<title>Result:</title>
		<para>
			The selected Domain is deleted.
		</para>
	</formalpara>
</section>